              <m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{F= \( 6 "." "67"` times `"10" rSup { size 8{ - "11"} } ` ital "Newton" -  ital "meter" rSup { size 8{2} } / ital "kg" rSup { size 8{2} }  \) ` \( m rSub { size 8{1} } `m rSub { size 8{2} }  \) `r rSup { size 8{ - 2} } } {}</m:annotation>
